# Baseline security headers — Netlify / Cloudflare Pages.
# (Vercel reads headers from vercel.json instead; other hosts set these at
# the CDN/server level.) A Content-Security-Policy is intentionally left out
# here because the inline theme-bootstrap script in index.html would need a
# matching hash/nonce — add it deliberately when you lock the deploy down.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
